    <item>
      <title>英国因车内有枪视频被曝光而撤换墨西哥大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/uk-removes-mexico-ambassador-after-video-surfaces-of-gun-in-car</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国驻墨西哥大使被悄然免职，因为一段五秒钟的视频在社交媒体上广为流传。视频中，他在一辆汽车里开玩笑地举起一把突击步枪并将其指向人们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/uk-removes-mexico-ambassador-after-video-surfaces-of-gun-in-car</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 16:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
